      "output": "\r\nModel                         Size Status\r\n-----                         ---- ------\r\nHGST HTS721010A9E630 1000202273280 OK    \r\nADATA SX6000NP        512105932800 OK    \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nERR: \r\n",
