ter: AndieKobbie-OMEN\r\n    Description: \r\n    Date: 2026-06-23T07:26:38.1990000Z\r\n>   Event ID: 19\r\n    Task: Agente di Windows Update\r\n    Level: Informazioni\r\n    Opcode: Installazione\r\n    Keyword: Installazione,Operazione completata\r\n    User: S-1-5-18\r\n    User Name: NT AUTHORITY\\SYSTEM\r\n    Computer: AndieKobbie-OMEN\r\n    Description: \r\n    Date: 2026-06-23T07:20:34.1250000Z\r\n>   Event ID: 1796\r\n    Task: N/A\r\n    Level: Errore\r\n    Opcode: Informazioni\r\n    Keyword: N/A\r\n    User: S-1-5-18\r\n    User Name: NT AUTHORITY\\SYSTEM\r\n    Computer: AndieKobbie-OMEN\r\n    Description: \r\n    Date: 2026-06-23T07:20:33.0660000Z\r\n>   Event ID: 1801\r\n    Task: N/A\r\n    Level: Errore\r\n    Opcode: Informazioni\r\n    Keyword: N/A\r\n    User: S-1-5-18\r\n    User Name: NT AUTHORITY\\SYSTEM\r\n    Computer: AndieKobbie-OMEN\r\n    Description: \r\n    Date: 2026-06-23T07:15:58.1170000Z\r\n>   Event ID: 18\r\n    Task: N/A\r\n    Level: Informazioni\r\n    Opcode: Informazioni\r\n    Keyword: N/A\r\n    User: S-1-5-18\r\n    User Name: NT AUTHORITY\\SYSTEM\r\n    Computer: AndieKobbie-OMEN\r\n    Description: \r\n    Date: 2026-06-23T07:15:29.0140000Z\r\n>   Event ID: 18\r\n    Task: N/A\r\n    Level: Informazioni\r\n    Opcode: Informazioni\r\n    Keyword: N/A\r\n    User: S-1-5-18\r\n    User Name: NT AUTHORITY\\SYSTEM\r\n    Computer: AndieKobbie-OMEN\r\n    Description: \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
